page.title: 13HOME LIFE
page.content: Most people get up at about seven o'clock and then they have breakfast.The things people can have include : Cornflakes, Special K, Rice Krispies, Bran Flakes, Coco Pops, Sultana Bran and Sugar Puffs. Most people have breakfast at about 7:45. They finish at about 8:00 and then watch television for about half an hour. They then go to the bathroom to clean their teeth and brush their hair. Most people who go to Carleton Green County Primary School live on the estate. The main road around the estate is Arundel Drive. There are about 500 houses on the estate. There are lots of different houses on the estate such as semi-detatched, detatched and bungalows.
